{"tid":1391792,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[放棄] 想自殺既人入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:07:09.000Z","uid":107157,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"adfe46fd83defef6f0143f91ce8be0423d9d317d","tid":1391792,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果 你 想 自 殺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔會阻止你地</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不過  </span> <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">  請等一等</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">約定</span></span>我地</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係香港革命<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完全失敗</span>既時候</span></span><br />\n<br />\n先至去尋死<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但 係 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係呢段時間</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你將會係一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完全無敵</span></span>既人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無野再可以失去</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔再有任何顧慮</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇敢</span></span>地去做你地想做既事</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">努力</span></span>去完成身為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人既使命</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非常肯定</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「約定之日」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對</span></span>唔會來臨 !</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為我地<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人</span>係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 永 不 言 敗 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">直到 革 命 成 功 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"0cb937ae2125d71dbe8f4f1cb22b461a0dc4cc1a","tid":1391792,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月3日 旺角遊行<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"ccfbe7f5f01b17f7a29c54df85807fbe9d203bca","tid":1391792,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"我想死"},{"pid":"327e3606f89626d5e4e4242139c572df72dad3e4","tid":1391792,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3fcfe8671c163d531d767652980304a0bd74ba","tid":1391792,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"多一個人都好重要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月3日 旺角遊行<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"791c5a12a30d4d035d4545b96de088c1015a1e3b","tid":1391792,"uid":63586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:21:58.000Z","msg":"死都要死得有價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db637e8ea27014bcb09e5206ed389fd05fe29759","tid":1391792,"uid"